reviewText: Contains topless views of Jenny in a bikini while fishing. She did catch and release a few fish, but more often her fishing lure brought in weeds.

If you want an instructional DVD, on learning how to catch fish, this isn't it. But, if you just want to kick back and watch a perky long legged blonde in a skimpy string bikini try for bass, then this DVD is definitely worth a look.

Jenny spends a leisurely afternoon out on a boat casting for bass and soaking up the sun. She seems to really enjoy fishing and being out on the lake, but can be easily distracted by bees, the possibility of prying eyes on shore, and her concern over tan lines. She actually does get a few bites on her line here and there, and Jenny isn't a bit shy about showing off her perkyness by removing her top, and working on that all important tan.
